dcterms:description: The Gorilla dataset consists of three parts - HuggingFace, TensorFlow, and PyTorch. The HuggingFace dataset is the most extensive, featuring over 925 unique APIs across 37 different domains, with each API having ten unique instructions. Each instance contains an instruction, domain, API call, explanation, and complete Python code to accomplish the task.
